2209  private static bool FilterApplyMethodBase(MethodBase methodBase, BindingFlags methodFlags, BindingFlags bindingFlags, CallingConventions callConv, Type[] argumentTypes)
2210  {
2211  bindingFlags ^= BindingFlags.DeclaredOnly;
2212  if ((bindingFlags & methodFlags) != methodFlags)
2213  {
2214  return false;
2215  }
2216  if ((callConv & CallingConventions.Any) == (CallingConventions)0)
2217  {
2218  if ((callConv & CallingConventions.VarArgs) != 0 && (methodBase.CallingConvention & CallingConventions.VarArgs) == (CallingConventions)0)
2219  {
2220  return false;
2221  }
2222  if ((callConv & CallingConventions.Standard) != 0 && (methodBase.CallingConvention & CallingConventions.Standard) == (CallingConventions)0)
2223  {
2224  return false;
2225  }
2226  }
2227  if (argumentTypes != null)
2228  {
2229  ParameterInfo[] parametersNoCopy = methodBase.GetParametersNoCopy();
2230  if (argumentTypes.Length != parametersNoCopy.Length)
2231  {
2232  if ((bindingFlags & (BindingFlags.InvokeMethod | BindingFlags.CreateInstance | BindingFlags.GetProperty | BindingFlags.SetProperty)) == BindingFlags.Default)
2233  {
2234  return false;
2235  }
2236  bool flag = false;
2237  if (argumentTypes.Length > parametersNoCopy.Length)
2238  {
2239  if ((methodBase.CallingConvention & CallingConventions.VarArgs) == (CallingConventions)0)
2240  {
2241  flag = true;
2242  }
2243  }
2244  else if ((bindingFlags & BindingFlags.OptionalParamBinding) == BindingFlags.Default)
2245  {
2246  flag = true;
2247  }
2248  else if (!parametersNoCopy[argumentTypes.Length].IsOptional)
2249  {
2250  flag = true;
2251  }
2252  if (flag)
2253  {
2254  if (parametersNoCopy.Length == 0)
2255  {
2256  return false;
2257  }
2258  if (argumentTypes.Length < parametersNoCopy.Length - 1)
2259  {
2260  return false;
2261  }
2262  ParameterInfo parameterInfo = parametersNoCopy[parametersNoCopy.Length - 1];
2263  if (!parameterInfo.ParameterType.IsArray)
2264  {
2265  return false;
2266  }
2267  if (!parameterInfo.IsDefined(typeof(ParamArrayAttribute), inherit: false))
2268  {
2269  return false;
2270  }
2271  }
2272  }
2273  else if ((bindingFlags & BindingFlags.ExactBinding) != 0 && (bindingFlags & BindingFlags.InvokeMethod) == BindingFlags.Default)
2274  {

2278  {
